Class ResultView

  • java.lang.Object
    • consoleUI.ResultView
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Controller

    public class ResultView
extends java.lang.Object
implements Controller
    ResultView - is a view only display on the console. The results from the games played are displayed here. Again no MVC pattern - initController is used to call other methods.
